    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="数字图像处理-MFC-第9周实验报告"><a href="#数字图像处理-MFC-第9周实验报告" class="headerlink" title="数字图像处理-MFC 第9周实验报告"></a>数字图像处理-MFC 第9周实验报告</h1><h2 id="代码-仅Resize-cpp，Resize-h，MFC002Dlg-cpp"><a href="#代码-仅Resize-cpp，Resize-h，MFC002Dlg-cpp" class="headerlink" title="代码(仅Resize.cpp，Resize.h，MFC002Dlg.cpp)"></a>代码(仅Resize.cpp，Resize.h，MFC002Dlg.cpp)</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-comment">// MFC002Dlg.cpp : implementation file</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 部分代码（OnButShow 和 OnBUTresize）</span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">CMFC002Dlg::OnButShow</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// <span class="hljs-doctag">TODO:</span> Add your control notification handler code here</span><br>    CDC *pDC = m_pic.GetDC();<br><br>    basicImagePro <span class="hljs-title function_">im</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;dog.bmp&quot;</span>)</span>;<br>    im.show(pDC);<br>    im.show_gray(pDC);<br>    <br>    ReleaseDC(pDC);<br>    <br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">CMFC002Dlg::OnBUTresize</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// <span class="hljs-doctag">TODO:</span> Add your control notification handler code here</span><br>    CDC *pDC = m_pic.GetDC();<br><br>    Resize <span class="hljs-title function_">im</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;dog.bmp&quot;</span>)</span>;<br>    im.mk_resize_img();<br>    im.show_resize(pDC);<br><br>    ReleaseDC(pDC);<br>    <br>&#125;<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br/><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-comment">// Resize.cpp: implementation of the Resize class.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////</span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;stdafx.h&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;MFC002.h&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Resize.h&quot;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">ifdef</span> _DEBUG</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">undef</span> THIS_FILE</span><br><span class="hljs-type">static</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> THIS_FILE[]=__FILE__;<br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> new DEBUG_NEW</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">endif</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">// Construction/Destruction</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////</span><br><br>Resize::Resize(<span class="hljs-type">char</span>* fn) : basicImagePro(fn)<br>&#123;<br>    resize_img = <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>;<br>    xn = <span class="hljs-number">0.8</span>;<br>    yn = <span class="hljs-number">0.5</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br>Resize::~Resize()<br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(resize_img) <span class="hljs-built_in">free</span>(resize_img);<br><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Resize::mk_resize_img</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// (1)</span><br>    <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i, j, h = _H(), w = _W();<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// (2)</span><br>    <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x_size = <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span>(w * xn)+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> y_size = <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span>(h * yn)+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// (3)</span><br>    resize_img = (<span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span>*)<span class="hljs-built_in">malloc</span>(x_size * y_size);<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// (4)</span><br>    <span class="hljs-type">double</span> kx = <span class="hljs-number">1.0</span> / xn; <br>    <span class="hljs-type">double</span> ky = <span class="hljs-number">1.0</span> / yn;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(j=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>; j&lt;y_size; j++)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i&lt;x_size; i++)&#123;<br>            resize_img[j*x_size + i] = gray_img[<span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span>(j * w * ky + i * kx)];<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Resize::show_resize</span><span class="hljs-params">(CDC* pDC)</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// (1)</span><br>    <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i, j, h = _H(), w = _W(), X = <span class="hljs-number">10</span>, Y = <span class="hljs-number">10</span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// (2)</span><br>    <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x_size = <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span>(w * xn) + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> y_size = <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span>(h * yn) + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// (3)</span><br>    <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span> R,G,B;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(j=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;j&lt;y_size; j++)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;x_size; i++)&#123;<br>            R = G = B = resize_img[j*x_size + i];<br>            pDC-&gt;SetPixel(i+X, j+Y, RGB(R,G,B));<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br><br>&#125;<br><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br/><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-comment">// Resize.h: interface for the Resize class.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////</span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> !defined(AFX_RESIZE_H__E358C62B_770E_43A9_A886_A5019F26E094__INCLUDED_)</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> AFX_RESIZE_H__E358C62B_770E_43A9_A886_A5019F26E094__INCLUDED_</span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> _MSC_VER &gt; 1000</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">pragma</span> once</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">endif</span> <span class="hljs-comment">// _MSC_VER &gt; 1000</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;basicImagePro.h&quot;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Resize</span> :</span> public basicImagePro  <br>&#123;<br>private:<br>    <span class="hljs-type">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-type">char</span>* resize_img;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">double</span> xn, yn;<br><br>public:<br>    Resize(<span class="hljs-type">char</span>*);<br>    virtual ~Resize();<br><br>public:<br>    <span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">show_resize</span><span class="hljs-params">(CDC*)</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">mk_resize_img</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span>;<br><br>&#125;;<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">endif</span> <span class="hljs-comment">// !defined(AFX_RESIZE_H__E358C62B_770E_43A9_A886_A5019F26E094__INCLUDED_)</span></span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></br></br></br></br></p><h2 id="点击“SHOW”按钮，触发图片的呈现以及灰度图像的覆盖："><a href="#点击“SHOW”按钮，触发图片的呈现以及灰度图像的覆盖：" class="headerlink" title="点击“SHOW”按钮，触发图片的呈现以及灰度图像的覆盖："></a>点击“SHOW”按钮，触发图片的呈现以及灰度图像的覆盖：</h2><p><img src="/1.png" alt="image"></p><h2 id="点击“Resize”按钮，实现图像大小的调整呈现："><a href="#点击“Resize”按钮，实现图像大小的调整呈现：" class="headerlink" title="点击“Resize”按钮，实现图像大小的调整呈现："></a>点击“Resize”按钮，实现图像大小的调整呈现：</h2><p><img src="/2.png" alt="image"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
